| comment "Dragnet [Ransomware]: dragnet-ransomware-2024-4268 — Mass File Rename (stormous)"
| comment "Status: experimental | Level: high | ID: 1b3537fd-b8df-5d6d-bdcb-535a6d338a25"
index=*
| where (file_path="*.encrypted" OR file_path="*.locked" OR file_path="*.ransom")
